About the Series:
Ruth Slater is released from prison after 15 years,having shot two policemen as a teenager,into 
a world that is new to her. 
She tells Carol,her probation officer she had a younger sister,Katie,eleven years her junior,
who was taken into care and adopted. 
Now known as Lucy she is a wild child living with middle-class couple Rachel and Michael Belcombe. Ruth visits her old home,whose new occupants,Izzie and John Ingram,unaware of her crime,offer to help her to find her sister.
Obtaining work at a meat-canning factory Ruth goes on her first adult date with workmate Brad,
but the Whelan brothers,sons of one of her victims,learn of her release and want revenge.

Staring : Peter Davison, Suranne Jones
